.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">499</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:211\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.211</biblScope></bibl>, Aristeas <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">297</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n77764.6\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">let pass</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καιρούς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0029.tlg001:1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Din.\">Din.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.36</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n77764.7\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔ με παρέβα φάσμα</foreign> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">escaped</tr_> me not, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg007.perseus-grc1:704\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hec.\">Hec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">704</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n77764.8\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pass on</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. εἰς ἀπέχθειαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:38:12:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plb.\">Plb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">38.12.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (sed leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προβῆναι</foreign>). </sense> 